<div class="jumbotron text-center">

  <h1>Hello world</h1>
  <p class="lead">I am Antti.</p>
  <h1>
    <a href="http://github.com/Sunave" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a>
  </h1>
  <img src="<%= asset_path('antti.jpg') %>" class="img-circle img-responsive">
</div>


<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h2 class="panel-title">Keywords and info</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-body">
    <p>I'm a computer science and usability enthusiast. My interests include</p>
    <h4>
      <% @tags.each do |tag| %>
        <span class="label label-default label"><i class="fa fa-slack"></i> <%= tag %></span>
      <% end %>
    </h4>

    <p>I live in Helsinki, Finland, where I'm studying Computer Science at University of Helsinki.</p>

    <h3>Contact:</h3>
    <div class="list-group-item"><i class="fa fa-github fa-lg fa-fw"></i> Check my Github projects at <strong><a href="http://github.com/Sunave" target="_blank">github.com/Sunave</a></strong></div>
    <div class="list-group-item"><i class="fa fa-envelope fa-lg fa-fw"></i> Contact by email <strong>my first name</strong> @ <strong>anttisuniala.fi</strong></div>
    <div class="list-group-item"><i class="fa fa-comments fa-lg fa-fw"></i> In IRC you can reach me via nick <strong>sunave</strong> at <strong>IRCnet</strong></div>
    <div class="list-group-item"><i class="fa fa-comment fa-lg fa-fw"></i> Or leave a comment below!</div>

  </div>
</div>


<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h3 class="panel-title">Posts by others</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-body">
    <div class="list-group">
      <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <h4 class="list-group-item-heading"><%= post.name %>:</h4>
        <div class="list-group-item"><%= post.message %></div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <%= render 'form' %>
  </div>
</div>




